<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="VOA20001025.2100.0295.mrg-E1" TYPE="IDENT">UN</COREF> Secretary General Kofi Annan</COREF> has <COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">nominated</COREF> <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">former Dutch Prime Minister Ruud Lubbers</COREF> as the new <COREF ID="VOA20001025.2100.0295.mrg-E1" TYPE="IDENT">UN</COREF> High Commissioner for Refugees .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Annan</COREF> praised <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">the record of <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">the 61 - year - old Mr. Lubbers</COREF> as a government leader , academic and private citizen</COREF> , *PRO*-1 saying 0 <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">this</COREF> made <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">him</COREF> the right man for the job .
